tip.text: Probably the best pizza I have ever had. The sour dough crust is amazing. Each pizza can feed two people.

Come in early so you can sample some of Gaytana's fine rums.

tip.text: Don't forget to read the Gettysburg Address, one of the most famous speeches ever spoken. It's on the left as you come in. Notice how it's written as a story. Lincoln was famous as a storyteller.
